ChangeLog: Briofita Vim Colorscheme
===================================

Github repository:
https://github.com/sonobre/briofita_vim

Vim Page:
http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=4136.


CHANGE LOG

NOTE: old change log entries related to previous Briofita features that
are deprecated as of June 2017, have been dropped from below list and are now
archived.

For more information about Briofita please check its companion Vim *help*
file. Provided Briofita has correctly been installed you just need enter
below command:

:help briofita

Version 4.1.0 (August, 2018)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Added a few more highlights. 
- Performed small enhancements / changes on few previously existing highlights.
- Added global variable "g:briofita_skip_termguicolor"; if it is NOT defined
  Briofita colorscheme will set termguicolor Vim option (for Vim versions
  starting with 8.0). 
  Otherwise, whatever the type of this global variable, termguicolor option
  will NOT be set by the colorscheme.
- Added global variable "g:briofita_skip_guicursor"; if it is NOT defined
  Briofita colorscheme will set the guicursor Vim option to an appropriate value.
  Otherwise, whatever the type of this global variable, guicursor option
  will NOT be set by the colorscheme.

Version 4.0.0 (June, 2017)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- New style, many new highlights.
- Lightline theme added.
- Improvements for many programming languages.
- Dropped previous' releases so-called "Briofita options" global variables.
- Dropped previous' releases highlight cycling feature.

Version 3.1.0 (March, 2014)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Bug fixes.
- Improvements highlight styles for C/C++, Perl, Python,
  Vim Help, Ruby, shellscript, VimL, diff, Asciidoc, PL/SQL,
  XML, HTML, Java, Manpage
- Added/changed Syntastic and TagList highlight customizations.
- Improvements in internal dictionary handling.

Version 3.0.8 (December, 2013)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Added a few topics and corrected some entries of the helpfile.

Version 3.0.7 (December, 2013)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Added five more VimL highlights.
- Added an EasyMotion highlight.
- Changed style of Diff, added DiffComment.
- Changed style of StatusLine highlight.
- Added highlights for Asciidoc, Html, NERDTree
  and Markdown, and changed style of XmlCommentPart.
- Changed or added highlight styles for: Asciidoc, Buffergator, Dirlist,
  C and C plus plus, Desktop files, FSTAB editing, Ruby, Vim Help, Html, Markdown,
  NERDTree, netrw (Explorer), Python, Restructured text (rst),
  Todo/Task plugins, Shellscript, Diff, VimL, CtrlP, ini-files,
  EasyMotion, Filesearch, Tabman, Make / M4.

Version 3.0.6 (October, 2013)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Colorscheme: Bug fix: corrected missing entry (in an internal list).
  Few changes for Asciidoc and Python syntaxes.
- Helpfile: Added a topic about cleared highlights (under Issues).

Version 3.0.5 (October, 2013)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 - Colorscheme: Improved highlights for Help, diffFile, Asciidoc,
   Search, XML, HTML, Awk, C, CSS, Ruby, Javascript, Markdown, NERD Tree,
   Perl, PL/SQL, SQL, Python, Sed, VimL.

Version 3.0.4 (October, 2013)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Colorscheme: Added highlights for Vim help, manpages and Python).
  Added special FoldColumn highlight for Normal black background.
  Improved several other highlights, including Vim Diff, Vim Help,
  Asciidoc, CSS, HTML, Java, Sed, manpage, Markdown, Perl,
  PL/SQL and Python.

Version 3.0.3 (August, 2013)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Improvements in Folded and Normal highlights.
  New Normal highlight with black background.
- Improved one of the Asciidoc highlights.

Version 3.0.2 (July, 2013)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Improved one highlight in the colorscheme (for HTML).

Version 3.0.1 (July, 2013)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Increased the release number/date.

Version 3.0.0 (July, 2013)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Extensive code refactoring and testing.
- Some highlights improved, some added.
- Bug fixes.

Version 2.0.3 (May, 2013)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Reduced contrasting background in a few highlights of these syntaxes:
  Sql,PL/SQL,Fountain,Vim Language.
 - Increased contrasting background of the IncSearch highlight.
- Corrections and improvements in the help text.

Version 2.0.2 (May, 2013)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Improved Search highlight. Cleaned help file.

Version 2.0.1 (May, 2013)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Code cleaning. Bug fix: corrected some leftovers from previous
  development.

Version 2.0.0 (May, 2013)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Increased major number. This version is not compatible with the previous one.
- Added a help file in the the "doc" sub-directory. Most of the text
  previously in the Vim online page has been moved into the help file.
- Improved highlights for several syntaxes.
- Internal highlights dictionary now split into small dictionaries
  for easier change.
- Suavization of style (less red, less high contrast).
- Bug fixes.
- Alternative folding highlights.

Version 1.5.0 (August, 2012)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Improved color highlights of a few elements.

Version 1.1 to v.1.4 (July, 2012)~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Bug fixes.

Version 1.0~
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- FIRST RELEASE (July, 2012)~
  Set red ICursor via 'guicursor' option.
  Designed for Vim GUI only, and Vim versions >= 7.3.

